cells.data:
Am currently setting up to do yet another project/training process which I will start May 1st. Have already logged where I am and will go back and look at what progress I have made at the end of May.

Mood is moderate - feeling slightly ill, but not too bad. Pain is fairly low today - took pain pill at 6am. Have pain specialist appointment next Wednesday morning. Will see what he says then.

Having lots of trouble sleeping, and some problems concentrating on my learning and projects. Maybe I am doing too much. Need to focus more on finance issues that are currently very bad, though we have a fair amount of money in the bank. 

Ate breakfast at Nats, going to walk over to Starbucks right now.
